</paragraph>
</caption>
<caption ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4690853" ID-Zenodo-Dep="4690853" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4690853/files/figure.png" pageId="46" pageNumber="47" startId="46.[151,259,1943,1967]" targetBox="[172,1415,182,1915]" targetPageId="46">
